<head>
   <title>

Multimedia CBT KnowledgeBase

</title>
</head>
<body text="#000000" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="../sand.gif">

<FORM ACTION=https://secure.computer.org/cgi-bin/cspress/shopcart.bat METHOD=POST>

<INPUT TYPE=Hidden NAME=catnumber VALUE="rs05735">

<blockquote>
<h2><br>

Multimedia CBT KnowledgeBase
<FONT SIZE="4"><SUP>&#153;  </SUP></FONT>

</h2>

<p>Serves potential users as well as potential manufacturers of multimedia
hardware and software. The ingredients of multimedia are: the global public
telephone network with broadband capability to transport bandwidth intensive
files, the PC with the capability to service multimedia applications, and
the overall system design that makes all of this computing transparent
to the user. The information technologies that it relies upon include text,
image, video, and voice processing.</p>

<p><i>Catalog # RS05735  &#151; $495.00</i></p>

</blockquote>

