1st International Workshop on High-Speed Network Computing (HiNet '95)

</h2>
<h3>

April 25, 1995  &#151;  Santa Barbara, CA

</h3>

<P><B>Partial List of Papers: </B>High-Speed Networking for Distributed
Multimedia Computing  •   Dynamic Load Balancing in a Message Passing
Virtual Parallel Machine  •   Enhanced PVM Communications Over a High-Speed
LAN  •   Faster Message Passing in PVM  •   Partitioning Strategies for
Multiplying Dense Matrices on Workstation Networks  •   A High-Speed
Document Retrieval Machine for Large Databases  •   DTMS: A Framework for
Multigrain Distributed Programming</P>

