Logic Synthesis • From High-Level Verification to (Low Level) Extraction
• Sequential Test Generation • Module Generators • Logic Synthesis • Memory
Testing • Design Environments and CAD Tools for Microsystems Design • Partitioning
in System Design • Synthesis and Testability • Novelties in Integrated
System Design • Modeling and Design Strategies for Microsystems Design
• New Technologies for Mixed-Signal Test • Recent Advances in Simulation
• DFT Solutions and IDDQ</p>

