<blockquote>
<h2><br>

14th IEEE VLSI Test Symposium (VTS '96)

</h2>
<h3>

April 28 - May 1, 1996 &#151; Princeton, NJ

</h3>

<p><b>Contents: </b>Design for Testability • Testability of Analog Circuits
• Synthesis for Testability • IDDQ Testing • On-Line Testing • Fault Diagnosis
and Dictionaries • Sequential Circuit Testing • Multi-Chip Modules and
Memory Testing • Delay Fault Testing • Advances in BIST • Fault Modeling
and Defect Coverage • Fault Simulation and Test Generation • Mixed Signal
Test Techniques</p>

<p><b><a href="../../conferen/proceed/vts96/toc.htm" target=_top>Abstracts</a></b></p>

<p><i>544 pages. Softcover. April 1996. ISBN 0-8186-7304-4. 
<br>Catalog # PR07304 &#151; $50.00 Members / $100.00 List</i></p>

</blockquote>

