<head>
   <title>

14th IEEE Symposium on Mass Storage Systems

</title>
</head>
<body text="#000000" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="../sand.gif">

<FORM ACTION=https://secure.computer.org/cgi-bin/cspress/shopcart.bat METHOD=POST>

<INPUT TYPE=Hidden NAME=catnumber VALUE="pr07064">

<blockquote>
<h2><br>

14th IEEE Symposium on Mass Storage Systems

<br><i><font SIZE=+0>Storage &#151; At the Forefront of Information 
Infrastructures</font></I></h2>

<h3>

September 11-14, 1995 &#151; Monterey, CA 

</h3>

<p><b>Contents: </b>New Requirements  •  Architectures  •  Data Access  •  War
Stories  •  Performance Modeling  •  Data at Work  •  Practical Experiences</p>

