</h2>
<h3>

February 26 - March 1, 1996 &#151; New Orleans, LA 

</h3>

<p><b>Contents: </b>Database Issues in Information Superhighways  •  Query
and Control in Multidatabase Systems  •  Temporal and Spatial Systems  •  Knowledge
Discovery  •  Mediation and Federated Databases  •  Relational Databases   •  
Distributed Information Systems and WWW  •  Visualization and Reverse Engineering
  •   Object-Oriented Databases &#151; Physical Organizations  •  Parallel Databases
  •   Workflow and Reengineering Case Studies  •  Object-Oriented Databases -
Design and Processing Techniques  •  Distributed information Systems  •  Multimedia
  •   Active Database/Knowledge Base Systems  •  Query Processing and Optimization
  •   Distributed Databases  •  Workflow and Groupware Systems  •  Multimedia -
Querying and Browsing  •  Scientific Databases &#151; Sequence Search Methods
  •   Workflow and Transaction Management  •  Multimedia &#151; Systems and Applications
  •   Object Standard</p>

