<head>
   <title>

SONET/SDH KnowledgeBase 
</title>
</head>
<body text="#000000" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="../sand.gif">

<FORM ACTION=https://secure.computer.org/cgi-bin/cspress/shopcart.bat METHOD=POST>

<INPUT TYPE=Hidden NAME=catnumber VALUE="rs04175">

<blockquote>
<h2><br>

SONET/SDH KnowledgeBase
<FONT SIZE="4"><SUP>&#153;  </SUP></FONT>
<br><font SIZE=+1> The Broadband Network Revolution </font> 

</h2>

<p>Presents the latest trends driving broadband networks, describes the
principles of WANs and broadband networks, and looks into SONET standards
and equipment. Also detailed are emerging synchronous optical networks,
SONET and broadband ISDN, and SONET topologies.</p>

<p><i>Catalog # RS04175  &#151; $349.00</i></p>

</blockquote>

