<blockquote>
<h2><br>

22nd EUROMICRO Conference '96  &#151 
<br><font size=+1><I>Beyond 2000: Hardware and Software Design Strategies</I></font>

</h2>
<h3>

September 2-5, 1996  &#151; Prague, CZECH REPUBLIC

</h3>

<p><b>Contents: </b> System-Level Design   •   Multiprocessor Architectures   •   Real-Time   •   Design Methodologies and Tools   •   Optimization   •   Development of Control Systems   •   Formal Methods for Hardware Design   •   Performance Engineering   •   Usability Engineering   •   Logic Synthesis   •   Fault Tolerance   •   Specification and Validation   •   Testing   •   Dependable Systems   •   High-Speed Networks   •   Memory Issues   •   Distributed Systems   •   Formal Specification   •   Coprocessors   •   Image Processing   •   Parallel Software Engineering   •   Operating Systems and Network Support   •   Novel Processor Architectures   •   Operational Considerations   •   Superscalar Architectures </p>

<p><i>690 pages. Softcover. September 1996. ISBN 0-8186-7487-3. 
<br>Catalog # PR07487  &#151; $75.00 Members / $150.00 List</i></p>

