<h2><br>

3rd International Conference Document Analysis and Recognition (ICDAR '95)

</h2>

<h3>

August 14-16,1995 &#151; Montreal, CANADA </h3>

<p><b>Contents: </b>Word Recognition •  Neural Networks •  Online Recognition
•  Application Systems •  Handwritten Character Recognition •  Segmentation
•  Image Processing Techniques •  Database and Document Retrieval •  Signature
Verification •  Model-Based Document Analysis •  Image Processing •  Map Interpretation
•  Classification Methods •  Document Understanding •  Feature Extraction
•  Reconstruction and Interpretation •  Document Structure and Analysis ·
Symbol Recognition •  Modeling Methods •  Shape Models •  Learning •  Layout
Analysis •  Storage and Retrieval</p>

<p><b><a href="../../conferen/proceed/icdar95/toc.htm" target=_top>Abstracts</a></b></p>


<p><i>1,264 pages. Softcover. August 1995. ISBN 0-8186-7128-9. 
