<DOCNO>WT27-B30-252</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA037-000720-B040-169</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://ada.computer.org:80/conferen/sc94/crovellam.html 206.99.235.18 19970111021831 text/html 55803
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Sat, 11 Jan 1997 02:24:58 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.5.2
Last-modified: Sat, 12 Nov 1994 02:16:58 GMT
