		</ul>

	<p>4.2 &nbsp; THE VLSI DESIGN METHODOLOGIES
	
		<ul>
		<p>4.2.1 &nbsp; FC VLSI 
				
			<ul>4.2.1.1 &nbsp; FC VLSI Silicon Technology
<br>4.2.1.2 &nbsp; FC VLSI GaAs Technology 
</ul>

<p>4.2.2 &nbsp; SC VLSI
		<br>4.2.3 &nbsp; GA VLSI
		<br>4.2.4 &nbsp; PL VLSI 
		<br>4.2.5 &nbsp; Summary of SC VLSI, GA VLSI, and PL VLSI.
		<br>4.2.6 &nbsp; ST VLSI</p>
	</ul></ul>

