<br>5.2.1.2 &nbsp; Random Test Vector Generation
<br>5.2 1.3 &nbsp; The SP and BIST Approaches for Sequential and       
                                 Combinational Circuits
<br>5.2.1.4 &nbsp; The SP Techniques
			</ul>
		
