</ul>

<p>6.2.6 &nbsp; UCB-RISC Addressing Mode
<br>6.2.7 &nbsp; UCB-RISC Register File Organization.
<br>6.2.8 &nbsp; UCB-RISC Processor Test Results 
		</ul>
	
<p>6.3 &nbsp; BASIC EXAMPLES: THE SU-MIPS
		
<ul>
<p>6.3.1 &nbsp; Structure of SU-MIPS Pipeline
<br>6.3.2 &nbsp; Performance Evaluation of SU-MIPS Processor. .
<br>6.3.3 &nbsp; Definition of Various Hazards

<ul>6.3.3.1 &nbsp; Resource Hazards 
