<DOCOLDNO>IA037-000718-B029-94</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://ada.computer.org:80/pubs/expert/1996/trends/x10010/java.htm 206.99.235.18 19970111034423 text/html 12188
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Sat, 11 Jan 1997 03:51:00 GMT
