And Promises For The Future.&quot; Masters Thesis, University of Phoenix, 1985.
</P>
<P>[20] Rothfeder, Jeffery. &quot;It's Late, Costly, Incompetent - But Try
Firing A Computer System.&quot; <I>Business Week.</I> (November 7, 1988).</P>

