<HEAD>
<TITLE> Design</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY><P>
 <HR> <A NAME=tex2html87 HREF=subsection3_3_1.html><IMG ALIGN=MIDDLE SRC="http://www.icase.edu/~haines/images/next_motif.gif"></A> <A NAME=tex2html85 HREF=hainesm.html><IMG ALIGN=MIDDLE SRC="http://www.icase.edu/~haines/images/up_motif.gif"></A> <A NAME=tex2html79 HREF=subsection3_2_2.html><IMG ALIGN=MIDDLE SRC="http://www.icase.edu/~haines/images/previous_motif.gif"></A>  <BR>
