<LI> <A NAME=tex2html91 HREF=subsection3_3_3.html#SECTION0003300000000000000> Remote Service Requests</A>
<LI> <A NAME=tex2html92 HREF=subsection3_3_4.html#SECTION0003400000000000000> Remote Thread Operations</A>
</UL>
