<FONT SIZE="2"><small><SUP>1</SUP></small> All essential interchange circuits and any others that are provided shall comply with the requirements of recommendation V.24. All interchange circuits indicated by X shall be properly terminated in the data equipment and in the data circuit-terminating equipment in accordance with the appropriate recommendation.<br>
