<table border=2 cellpadding=5>
<caption>Table 1. The ever-shrinking length of successive ages correlates with accelerating technology.</caption>

<th><tr><td align=center><br><b>Age</b></td><td align=center><b><br>Length, T yrs (term)</b></td><td align=center><b>Rate of interaction,<br>R mph (technology)</b></td><td align=center><b>Time to circle Earth, yrs
