<DOCNO>WT27-B30-371</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA035-000700-B049-207</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://ada.computer.org:80/cspress/catalog/bp07644/imgu-pre.htm 206.99.235.18 19970110214706 text/html 8419
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Fri, 10 Jan 1997 21:53:43 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.5.2
Last-modified: Fri, 21 Jun 1996 00:10:44 GMT
Content-type: text/html
