<h2>About the Author</h2>
<p><b>Belur V. Dasarathy</b> is a senior principal engineer at Dynetics, Inc. His current research and development interests include sensor fusion, pattern recognition, image analysis, fuzzy logic, neural networks, data compression, machine intelligence, and related topics. He is actively engaged in the design and development of automated intelligent decision systems as applied to a broad spectrum of multispectral and multisensor environments arising in various strategic and tactical DOD applications. In addition, he has previously authored <I>Decision Fusion</I> (IEEE Computer Society Press, 1994) and <I>Nearest Neighbor Norms: NN Pattern Classification Techniques</I> (IEEE Computer Society Press, 1991).</p>

