<h2>About the Author</h2>
<p><b>Dale Karolak</b> is currently a Design Engineering Manager at TRW Automotive Electronics Group. He received his Ph.D. in Software Engineering from Union Institute in Cincinnati, Ohio and his M.B.A.. from the University of Phoenix, Phoenix, Arizona. His research interests include software engineering management, software process development, software architectures, and software verification/validation. He has published numerous papers for IEEE, ACM, SERF, NSIA, and has a patent pending on a Software Architecture for a Communications (Network) Management System.</p>

