<table border=2 cellpadding=5>
<caption><b>Table 2. Features of the ages.</b></caption>

<th><tr><td align=center colspan=5><b> Machine Age</b></td></tr>
<tr><td align=center><b>Feature</b></td><td align=center><b>Agrarian</b></td><td align=center><b>Industrial</b></td><td align=center><b>Post-industrial</b></td><td align=center><b>Info</b></td></tr></th>

<tr><td><i>Basic value</i></td>

<td>Land, human labor, livestock</td>

<td>Weight, size, energy</td>

<td>Efficiency, speed</td>

<td>Information</td></tr>

<tr><td><i>Symbol of power</i></td>

<td>Land ownership, might</td>

<td>Material possessions</td>

<td>Organizational skill</td>

<td>Fashion, currency, popularity</td></tr>


<tr><td><i>Means of production</i></td>

<td>Individual craftsmanship</td>

<td>Hierarchical, large-group, mass production</td>

<td>Networked, small-group projects, flexible production</td>

<td>Individual craftsmanship, flexible production</td></tr>

<tr><td><i>Means of distribution</i></td>

<td>Individual barter</td>

<td>Large-group distribution channels</td>
