<DOCNO>WT27-B30-404</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA036-000710-B023-165</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://ada.computer.org:80/pubs/expert/1996/trends/x5010/cohen.htm 206.99.235.18 19970111011443 text/html 22187
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Sat, 11 Jan 1997 01:21:18 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.5.2
Last-modified: Tue, 22 Oct 1996 18:55:36 GMT
Content-type: text/html
