<DOCHDR>
http://ada.computer.org:80/pubs/expert/1996/insight/x4013/x4013.htm 206.99.235.18 19970111012016 text/html 20300
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Sat, 11 Jan 1997 01:26:48 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.5.2
Last-modified: Wed, 28 Aug 1996 22:35:54 GMT
